02:16.208 --> 02:17.458
<i>Okay.</i>

02:17.541 --> 02:19.125
<i>I'm relieved to hear that, Dad.</i>

02:26.458 --> 02:29.458
COUNTDOWN TO SONGKRAN DAY
13TH APRIL

02:45.666 --> 02:46.500
Thida.

03:02.125 --> 03:02.958
Wanchai.

03:04.750 --> 03:05.583
Thida.

03:08.291 --> 03:09.666
Listen to me.

03:13.958 --> 03:15.833
Your brother was a good man.

03:18.916 --> 03:21.416
I don't regret loving Jo.

03:25.166 --> 03:26.708
I miss him.

03:57.083 --> 03:58.083
Jo.

03:58.166 --> 03:59.166
Yes.

04:03.083 --> 04:04.666
Suppose I got pregnant.

04:06.000 --> 04:07.083
What would you say?

04:31.250 --> 04:33.500
