04:56.291 --> 04:57.833
I just found out today.

05:16.291 --> 05:17.750
Let's get away from here.

05:18.750 --> 05:19.583
Okay?

05:34.666 --> 05:35.916
I'm happy.

05:37.666 --> 05:39.958
