05:53.083 --> 05:57.875
3 MONTHS AGO

06:00.000 --> 06:01.208
MR. MAN

06:02.791 --> 06:05.333
Hold on. I have to take this.

06:12.791 --> 06:14.916
-Yes, Mr. Man.
<i>-Hello, Jo.</i>

06:15.000 --> 06:17.291
Come see me at Magnolia tonight.

06:17.875 --> 06:19.375
