06:24.083 --> 06:27.375
-He's just arriving.
<i>-I have stuff to deliver, don't I?</i>

06:27.458 --> 06:29.333
<i>Why are you making such a fuss?</i>

06:29.916 --> 06:32.750
Let's give him a tour.
I'll show him the world.

06:32.833 --> 06:33.666
Hey.

06:46.541 --> 06:47.875
