07:27.416 --> 07:28.291
I guarantee

07:28.375 --> 07:30.458
-you've never had this before.
-Thank you.

07:30.541 --> 07:31.750
Let me just make sure.

07:31.833 --> 07:32.666
Sure.

07:34.416 --> 07:35.333
How is it?

07:35.958 --> 07:37.750
It's so tender. It's really delicious.

07:37.833 --> 07:40.208
