-Wow.

07:47.208 --> 07:48.083
Motherfucker.

07:48.583 --> 07:51.166
-Are you blind?
-Wait. Hold on.

07:51.250 --> 07:52.583
I'm so sorry, Mr. Man.

07:52.666 --> 07:54.541
Butt out. It's none of your business.

07:54.625 --> 07:55.583
