-Calm down.

08:05.291 --> 08:06.541
Mr. Man, wait!

08:08.333 --> 08:10.875
Calm down. You know who Mr. Man is.

08:10.958 --> 08:13.791
-Fuck that. Don't give him my dad's money.
-Wait.

08:15.166 --> 08:16.041
Just take it.

08:18.208 --> 08:19.458
-Come on.
-Wait.

08:20.458 --> 08:21.541
Take my glass too.

08:21.625 --> 08:24.166
Take his glass. Just be done with it.

08:24.250 --> 08:26.125
Go!

08:26.208 --> 08:29.375
-Don't let me see your face again!
-Hey.

08:30.166 --> 08:31.333
You're late.

08:32.666 --> 08:35.083
I heard from Hardcore
that you have a girl.

08:36.958 --> 08:38.166
You believe that lunatic?

08:39.708 --> 08:41.791
I don't care if you have a girl.

08:41.875 --> 08:43.125
Just don't let it affect your work.

08:47.125 --> 08:47.958
Shit.

08:48.625 --> 08:50.666
-Is that your car?
-Yes.

08:52.291 --> 08:53.708
I'll tell you what.

08:53.791 --> 08:55.416
If this job goes well,

08:57.000 --> 08:58.583
I'll reward you handsomely.

08:59.291 --> 09:01.166
Then you can get a new car.

09:01.250 --> 09:02.583
That's an eyesore.

09:04.583 --> 09:06.666
You should be careful.

09:07.500 --> 09:08.750
If your father finds out…

09:10.916 --> 09:12.625
How will my father find out

09:12.708 --> 09:13.958
if you don't tell him?

09:17.166 --> 09:19.541
If I tell him, I'll get in trouble too.

09:21.833 --> 09:22.666
You got that right.

09:23.583 --> 09:25.291
There, that's my car.

09:25.791 --> 09:26.750
The stuff is inside.

09:27.500 --> 09:28.333
Let's go.

09:42.333 --> 09:43.541
