09:46.333 --> 09:47.791
Let's fucking go!

09:51.583 --> 09:53.250
Faster!

09:58.458 --> 10:00.916
Damn, it's so powerful.

10:03.583 --> 10:05.958
That's what I'm talking about.

10:06.041 --> 10:09.333
HAVE YOU MADE UP YOUR MIND
ABOUT GIVING ME INFORMATION?

10:13.833 --> 10:14.791
THIDA SENT A PHOTO

10:22.041 --> 10:23.458
REPLY. DELETE.

10:24.333 --> 10:25.666
What is that clunker?

10:25.750 --> 10:30.791
Is that a piece of junk you're driving?
Is this as fast as you can go? Fuck you.

10:37.000 --> 10:38.875
<i>I'm ready to give you
info on Ruampalangjai.</i>

10:45.583 --> 10:50.000
<i>But I need money and assurance
that my identity will be protected.</i>

10:55.916 --> 11:00.166
Hey, asshole, now you're swerving.

11:00.250 --> 11:01.958
Jo, look at them. What a pussy.

11:04.125 --> 11:05.458
IF YOU'RE READY, CONTACT ME.

11:07.416 --> 11:08.500
Hey!

11:08.583 --> 11:09.833
Jo.

11:09.916 --> 11:11.458
You're ratting on me?

11:11.541 --> 11:14.375
-No. What do you mean? Give me that.
-Who's this fucking reporter?

11:14.458 --> 11:16.125
Fuck you, Jo!

11:16.208 --> 11:18.958
-I'm driving, asshole.
-Give it to me!

11:21.791 --> 11:23.125
Watch out!

11:25.041 --> 11:25.916
-Shit.
-Hey!

13:18.708 --> 13:20.916
I almost caught pneumonia waiting for you.

13:21.750 --> 13:22.916
Right, Em?

13:32.708 --> 13:36.416
Goodbye for real this time, honey.

13:52.708 --> 13:53.666
Fuck you.

13:53.750 --> 13:54.583
Son of a bitch.

13:56.500 --> 13:57.875
Who gave the order?

13:58.833 --> 14:00.333
Lackeys like you

14:01.000 --> 14:03.750
