has to give the order.

14:06.833 --> 14:07.666
Wanchai.

14:11.333 --> 14:13.416
I'm sorry that I couldn't help Thida.

14:16.833 --> 14:17.666
So…

14:18.791 --> 14:20.375
why are you helping me?

14:22.083 --> 14:23.208
Jo was my friend.

14:24.916 --> 14:25.958
We talked about everything.

14:29.208 --> 14:30.916
We wanted to escape this shitty life.

14:32.625 --> 14:34.041
<i>Everything Jo did,</i>

14:34.708 --> 14:36.416
<i>these scumbags told him to do.</i>

14:40.500 --> 14:41.666
You asshole.

14:41.750 --> 14:42.625
You ingrate.

14:43.833 --> 14:46.416
You'll meet your end, motherfucker.

14:48.750 --> 14:51.291
But I think you'll meet
your end first, Hardcore.

14:52.083 --> 14:53.291
Tell him.

14:54.333 --> 14:55.166
That day,

14:55.875 --> 14:56.958
what happened to Jo?

15:01.291 --> 15:02.416
Answer me, asshole!

15:05.875 --> 15:07.416
It was him that night, wasn't it?

15:09.000 --> 15:11.708
<i>He took the driver
of the sports car away on his motorcycle.</i>

15:13.708 --> 15:14.666
It was this fucker.

15:17.041 --> 15:18.291
Yes.

15:18.375 --> 15:20.166
That's right. Fuck you.

15:21.125 --> 15:23.208
He helped Wat's
piece-of-shit son, Man, escape,

15:24.166 --> 15:25.875
<i>and he left Jo behind to take the blame.</i>

15:27.000 --> 15:27.958
That's why, when we got there,

15:29.208 --> 15:30.333
